<section class="content">
  <div class="col-1">
    <h2>Hi, I'm Andrea.</h2>
    <p class="nickname">You can call me Andi.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="col-2">
    <%= image_tag("amignolo-profile-web.jpg", :class => "bio") %>
    <p>I founded method & matter because I believe in leaders like you. Leaders that don't necessarily "look" like the dominant leadership archetype. The early years of my leadership journey were fraught with doubt, derision, and failures as I struggled to find a way of leading that was aligned with my values and vision. With the guidance of an executive coach, I began unwinding beliefs that no longer served me while cultivating a connection with my power, purpose, and unique way of leading.

    <p>The work was nothing less than transformational -  and I want this for you, too.  </p>

    <p>Before becoming a coach I lead product and design teams for startups in the B2B SaaS space, and before that I taught business English in Japan for four years. I'm currently the President of the <%= link_to('Interaction Design Association', 'https://ixda.org') %>, have an MBA from the  <%= link_to('Weatherhead School of Management', 'https://weatherhead.case.edu') %>, a BA in Technocultural Studies from <%= link_to('Oberlin College', 'https://oberlin.edu') %>, and am a Professional Certified Coach through the <%= link_to('The International Coaching Federation', 'https://coachingfederation.org/') %>.

    <p><strong>Land Acknowledgement:</strong> I reside on the unceded ancestral homeland of the <%= link_to('Ramaytush Ohlone', 'https://www.ramaytush.org') %> peoples who are the original inhabitants of the San Francisco Peninsula. With deepest respect to the Ancestors, Elders and Relatives of the Ramaytush Community, I affirm their sovereign rights as First Peoples. I am committed to dismantling ongoing legacies of settler colonialism and white supremacy through study, service, donations, Yunakin Land Tax, and my own inner-work. </p>

