  </div>

  <div class="col-2">
    <p>I am passionate about working with people, teams, and companies who are committed to creative ways of leading (and living) in this volatile and uncertain world. People who believe that business can be an instrument for positive change and that work can be filled with intention, meaning, and joy. If you are longing to live at the intersection of purpose and passion, if you are ready to take the next giant step in your leadership journey, and if you are ready to listen deeply to what is calling to you, <%= link_to("let's talk", 'consultation' )%>.</p>

    <p>At a glance, people I work with tend to be:</p>

    <ul class="bullets">
      <li>Non-founder executives - C-level, EVP, SVP, VP</li>
      <li>Executive teams</li>
      <li>Global management teams</li>
      <li>Pre-seed to IPO start-ups & scale-ups</li>
      <li>Social entrepreneurs</li>
      <li>Senior ICs (staff, prinicpal)</li>
      <li>Emerging leaders (senior manager - director level) in design, product management, and engineering</li>
